{
  "texts": [
    "Students usually tend to search information or ideas from the internet and they do it the same way in using AI tools.",
    "They only search ideas for their written content.",
    "However, the students are not comfortable to use AI in writing composition despite the idea that these tools can help them to produce written outputs instantly.",
    "They also disagree on the statements that AI tools can produce quality outputs and are used as a compliment in their writing process.",
    "This means that students are not fully-aware on the use of AI."
  ]
}